## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all cultural perspectives on memorials. Additionally, the psychological impact of memorials can vary significantly among individuals, making it challenging to generalize the findings. Further research, including empirical studies and cross-cultural analyses, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the significance of memorials.

